import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { BorderBox, Image, ResponsiveImage } from '../src'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"image"}}>{`Image`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"default-image"}}>{`Default Image`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Image src="https://picsum.photos/110/110/?random" />`} __scope={{props,BorderBox,Image,ResponsiveImage}}>
  <Image src="https://picsum.photos/110/110/?random" />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"custom-size"}}>{`Custom size`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Image
  width="300px"
  height="200px"
  src="https://picsum.photos/300/300/?random"
/>`} __scope={{props,BorderBox,Image,ResponsiveImage}}>
  <Image
    width="300px"
    height="200px"
    src="https://picsum.photos/300/300/?random"
  />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"responsive-image"}}>{`Responsive image`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<BorderBox maxWidth="400px" width="100%" height="auto" p={0}>
  <ResponsiveImage src="https://picsum.photos/400/250/?random" />
</BorderBox>`} __scope={{props,BorderBox,Image,ResponsiveImage}}>
  <BorderBox maxWidth="400px" width="100%" height="auto" p={0}>
    <ResponsiveImage src="https://picsum.photos/400/250/?random" />
  </BorderBox>
</Playground></MDXTag>
